            <td class="about"><h2>Standalone Power</h2><br>
                Trackover came up in the process of creating a standalone tracking device that has the ability
                to charge itself with a separate power supply. While the phone is turned off, user will be able
                to track the location and determine whether it’s on the move or still. Trackover will provide
