                track the SIM details and notify the user when the SIM is removed or replaced without depending
                on the mobile phone’s battery. <br>
                <h2>Hard Cover</h2><br>
                This device will be set to a screw type phone cover. The cover will be fixed to the phone with a
                specific type of screws thereby making it difficult for a person to remove it in real time providing
                the device enough time to deliver all the information to the respective user. <br>
                <h2>Data Encrypting</h2><br>
                When the person realizes that his/her phone is stolen/misplaced, first he/she can encrypts the data
                and valuable files that he/she has in the phone. User can simply send a message to the SIM in the
                mobile phone. This message activates the device’s encrypting process. <br>
                <h2>GPS Tracking</h2><br>
                This device uses its own SIM card so that the user can track down the smartphone using this SIM number.
                This allows the user to track the mobile phone even when it’s being switched off or having a swapped SIM.
                When the mobile phone is lost or stolen, GPS will work even when the device is not connected to the internet. <br>
